text: Rahmonali Barotov (born on 10 March 1987) is a Tajikistani footballer who plays for Regar-TadAZ Tursunzoda. He is a member of the Tajikistan national football team in the 2010 FIFA World Cup qualification campaign. ==International goals== {| class="wikitable" ! # !! Date !! Venue !! Opponent !! Score !!
